We match  each games city or do a look up with the corresponding country from the second table:

Mapping:
       games

Year	City	Country

1896	Athens	Greece
1948	London	UK
2004	Athens	Greece
2008	Beijing	China
2012	London	UK


SELECT g.Year, g.City, c.country FROM Games g JOIN City c on g.city = c.name;

Answer:
Greece, UK, Greece, China, UK

